UKHALE ngokungalandelwa kwemigomo ebekelwe ukulwa neCovid-19 kuleli umengameli Cyril Ramaphosa ememezela ukuthi iNingizimu Afrika ibuyela esigabeni sesithathu sikathaqa ngoMsombuluko ebusuku. UMengameli wethule inkulumo esizweni kulandela ukunyuka kwesibalo sabantu abatheleleke ngeCovid-19 muva nje kuleli. Sebengaphezulu kuka 1 million abantu asebeke bahaqeka ngeCovid-19 kuleli. Ngesikhathi ethula inkulumo yakhe uRamaphosa ukhale ngabantu asebeyekile ukusebenzisa izibulali magciwane, ukugeza izandla, kanye nabantu abangazifaki izifonyo. Uthe ukungalandelwa kwale migomo yikho okusabalalalisa ngesivinini iCovid-19 kuleli. URamaphosa uthe kusukela kusasa izwe lizobuyela esigabeni sesithathu sikathaqa ukuze kwehle izinga lokusabalala kwe-Covid-19 kuleli. Isigaba sesithathu sihambisana nokwehliswa kwesibalo sabantu abahambela imicimb; imingcwabo kumele ihanjelwe abantu abawu-50 kuphela. Amabhizinisi kumele abeke isibalo sabantu abazovumeleka ukungena emsebenzini. Izindawo ezidayisa utshwala zivaliwe kanti nokuphuza utshwala ezindaweni zomphakathi njengasebhishi nasemapaki kuvaliwe. Ukuthutha utshwala nakho kuvaliwe. URamaphosa uthe oNgqongqoshe abayingxenye yesigungu esibhekelela ukulwa neCovid-19 bazochaza kabanzi ngeminye imithetho ethinta isigaba sesithathu. URamaphosa uthe izwe lizohlala esigabeni sesithathu kuze kushaye uJanuwari 15. Uthe emasontweni azayo bazoqapha ukuthi isabalala kangakanani iCovid-19. Uthe kulindeleke ukuthi umgomo weCovid-19 uqale ukusatshalaliswa kuleli ngekota yesibili ngonyaka ozayo.